main event: A civilian observer reported three round white objects in the sky that remained visible for approximately two hours on July 7, 1961.
interesting points: Objects were not in formation,Two of the three objects departed in a northwest direction while one remained, The sighting occurred at 38 degrees 57 minutes N, 119 degrees 57 minutes W, No sound or unusual features were associated with the objects, No other reports of the sighting were received through local sheriff's office or base facilities.
